nteresting output.\r\n\r\nBtw, you do have an Oracle client installed, do you?	1.9.3	shortcutter@googlemail.com	2009-02-05 13:57:00	Robert	Klemme	2012-05-02 12:52:22.703637	2012-05-03 23:04:56.349536
